cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single image haze removal. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of a generative adversarial network (GAN) also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), and the use of predictive models could suggest cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the importance of diversity in the dataset used for training, which could suggest cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
